{
  "texts": [
    "To solve this critical gap for our community, we propose FLAME, which provides the following novel contributions:",
    "We release an open-source software for creating standardized pipelines for LM evaluations for core financial NLP tasks.",
    "Our configurable pipeline (see Figure 2) handles the complete evaluation process.",
    "Large-Scale Model Assessment: We conduct extensive evaluations of 23 open-weight and proprietary LMs, exposing strengths and weaknesses across 20 financial benchmarks (see Figure 1).",
    "We provide a meta-analysis of the results, including a study on the performance/cost trade-off space."
  ]
}